column5: Is there any bait shops near Alcona?  Thankyou.
Yes. there's a place called Love2fish 705-456-8745, located near Lefroy(Belly wart).
There's bait IN Alcona......lol......Paulyanna,(Jerry) has his shack at the end of the 9th lines ......minnows and hut rentals.....
Got mine 5 bucks for two scoops (of raisins) at the end of 10th line at the restaurant.
